Reso
├─ PRD
│ ├─ Overview
│ │ ├─ One-liner: Reso guides intrusive thoughts into a 3-minute, private, structured session.
│ │ ├─ Problem: Spirals → rumination
│ │ ├─ Users & JTBD: Overthinkers. “When spiraling, help me reframe fast so I feel calmer.”
│ │ └─ Value: Short, frictionless reframing
│ ├─ Success Metrics
│ │ ├─ North Star: % users completing ≥1 guided session/day.
│ │ └─ Guardrails: Completion ≥70%, median session 1–4 min, D7 ≥25%, crash-free ≥99.5%, MobSF High=0.
│ ├─ Scope
│ │ ├─ In: Guided framework (10 prompts), Accept/Fight branch, tags, mood before/after, summary, history, autosave/restore, local-only, system theme.
│ │ └─ Out: Accounts/sync, AI assist, exports, reminders (later).
│ ├─ User Flows
│ │ ├─ Home → Start → Q1–Q10 (branch at step 8) → Summary → Save.
│ │ ├─ Home → History → Detail → Delete.
│ │ ├─ Resume draft on reopen.
│ │ └─ Search by tag/text.
│ ├─ Functional Requirements
│ │ ├─ Progress indicator
│ │ ├─ Tag (preset/custom)
│ │ └─ Summary: next step + quote.
│ ├─ Non-Functional
│ │ ├─ Offline-first
│ │ ├─ Accessibility (dynamic type, screen reader labels).
│ │ └─ Privacy: local SQLite only
│ ├─ Data Model (SQLite)
│ │ ├─ sessions(id, created_at, updated_at, tag, path('accept'|'fight'), mood_before, mood_after, summary)
│ │ └─ session_answers(id, session_id FK, step 1..10, question, answer)
│ ├─ UX & Content
│ │ ├─ Tone: brief, non-judgmental.
│ │ └─ Copy: 1–2 short sentences per prompt, subtle haptics on step/save.
│ ├─ Risks & Assumptions
│ │ ├─ Risk: flow fatigue → keep under 3 min, show progress, allow skip.
│ │ └─ Assumption: brief guided writing reduces rumination.
│ ├─ Release Criteria
│ │ ├─ No dead ends
│ │ └─ MobSF High=0
│ ├─ QA Checklist
│ ├─ Start/complete both paths
│ ├─ History CRUD
│ ├─ Theme follows system
│ └─ No network requests in v0.x.
├─ SLC
│ ├─ v0.1 — Core Flow
│ │ ├─ Goals: Ship guided session end-to-end with history
│ │ ├─ Screens: Home, Session (stepper), Summary, History(list/detail), About.
│ │ ├─ Data: SQLite schema + DAO
│ │ ├─ Acceptance: Complete both paths
│ │ └─ Done When: Crash-free ≥99.5%, cold start <1s, MobSF High=0.
│ ├─ v0.2 — Momentum
│ │ ├─ Features: Local reminders
│ │ ├─ Acceptance: Schedule/cancel reminder
│ │ └─ Done When: Reminder fires reliably offline
│ ├─ v0.3 — Safety & Share
│ │ ├─ Features: App lock (PIN/biometric)
│ │ ├─ Acceptance: Lock on reopen
│ │ └─ Done When: Lock latency <1s
│ ├─ v0.4 — Insight
│ │ ├─ Features: Weekly summary (counts, top tags, mood delta), lightweight streaks.
│ │ ├─ Acceptance: Summary card accurate
│ │ └─ Done When: Calculations verified on sample data
│ └─ v1.0 — Assist & Sync (optional)
│ ├─ Features: AI suggestions (opt-in)
│ ├─ Acceptance: Data never sent without consent
│ └─ Done When: Sync conflict-free
├─ Engineering
│ ├─ Stack: Expo RN (Router, Paper, Reanimated, Haptics), SQLite
│ ├─ Releases: version in app.config.ts
│ ├─ Security & MobSF: HTTPS none (no network v0.x)
│ └─ Accessibility: Labels, focus order, contrast AA, dynamic type.
└─ Appendix
├─ Prompt Copy (Accept/Fight)
├─ Tag Presets (e.g., relationship, career, family, health, finance, self-esteem)
└─ About/Privacy Copy (“All data is stored locally on your device. No cloud sync.”)


